    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Open-air amphitheaters built during the Nazi era in Germany for Völkisch meetings and to view theater and propaganda presentations. Some 1200 sites were planned but only about 40 were built.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
